707007f-a.title: Brooklyn: Surf Ave. - 36th St. W.
707007f-a.text:
Surf Ave., west from West 36th to 37th Streets, showing the entrance to
Sea Gate. The Sea View Hotel, operated by Mc Pherson stood at the left near
the entrance in 18657
January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REE ODUCED.
